parameters:
\SE[0]Oh... um... let me see... \SE[1]If I remember
correctly... you're Vega-chan, right? \SE[0]Is there
something you don't understand?
\SE[90] (It's become quite popular to call me Vega-chan....)

\SE[2] (I had heard that my bust size was big... but indeed,
it's even larger than I imagined...)
\SE[3] (Alright, there doesn't seem to be anyone around...)

\SE[4]I'll get straight to the point. \.I came here to help
you. \!\SE[3]It's at the request of Laura from the village
of Hatayaki. \!\SE[2]...Does that name sound familiar to
you?

\SE[3]It doesn't seem like a case of mistaken
identity.... \SE[50]And also... Melissa and Lunaroa. These
two were particularly worried about you. \SE[3]...With this,
do you think you can trust me?

\SE[12]...I understand. I will trust you. \SE[3] Can you
please tell me more about it?

\SE[2]Yes, gladly. \.There is one more person, a comrade.
\!\SE[3]Let's include them in the conversation as well.
